    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary motorcar, maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This vehicle transcends the standard pre-owned category, offering a flawless exterior luster paired with an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been preserved to meet the requirements of the most discerning collector. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a definitive example of automotive excellence, characterized by its pristine state and uncompromising performance profile.",
