    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its flawless original factory paint which remains protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Step inside to an interior that still carries that crisp new-car aroma; the premium leather upholstery is supple and entirely free of creases, scuffs, or wear. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is peerless, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by authorized technicians. With zero accidents, a clean title, and exceptionally low mileage, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in essentially 'out-of-the-box' condition. It drives with the precision and smoothness of the day it first left the assembly line. No scratches, no dings, and no compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
